"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:2.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">2.2</span> 標題：甩石機弦（sling）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מַרְגֵּמָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： margemah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:8\">PRO 26:8</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： קלע, קֶלַע, קַלָּע</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： qala‘（動詞或名詞）, qela‘)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:16\">JDG 20:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:40\">1SA 17:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:49\">1SA 17:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:50\">1SA 17:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam25:29\">1SA 25:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs3:25\">2KI 3:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:14\">2CH 26:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:20\">JOB 41:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:15\">ZEC 9:15</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： σφενδόνη, σφενδονήτης</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： sfendonē, sfendonētēs)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt6:12\">JDT 6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt9:7\">JDT 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir47:4\">SIR 47:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc6:51\">1MA 6:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc9:11\">1MA 9:11</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0379_sling.jpg\" alt=\"投石器和圓形彈弓石（亞述展廊（Assyrian Gallery），大英博物館）\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">投石器和圓形彈弓石（亞述展廊（Assyrian Gallery），大英博物館） (Gary Todd, worldhistorypics.weebly.com, CC0)</figcaption></figure>在一塊不大的長方形或橢圓形皮革或布料兩端繫上繩索，即製成甩石機弦。皮革或布料比人的手掌略小一點，繩索則大約是人手臂的長度。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0380_slings_hant.jpg\" alt=\"揮舞甩石機弦的士兵\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">揮舞甩石機弦的士兵 (© Mike Peel (www.mikepeel.net)., CC BY-SA 4.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>甩石機弦用來將石頭高速擲向目標。石頭放在皮革或布料形成的小袋內，投擲的人緊握兩根繩索的末端，並快速劃圈揮舞石頭，在算準的時刻放開其中一條繩索，石頭就會急速飛向目標。要用甩石機弦精準地擲中目標，需經長期練習。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>翻譯者在選擇譯詞時，應該避免讓讀者以為甩石機弦是用多根橡膠製成的現代彈弓。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:14\">2CH 26:14</a> 、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:20\">JOB 41:20</a> （《和》41:28）和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:15\">ZEC 9:15</a> 中，焦點其實是在石頭，而不在武器。在這些經文中，翻譯者可能要避免提及甩石機弦；例如，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:28\">JOB 41:28</a> b（《和》41:20）可以譯成，「擲向他的石頭就像碎稭一樣」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 直譯）。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt6:12\">JDT 6:12</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc9:11\">1MA 9:11</a> 中，希臘文<em>sfendonētēs</em> 不是描述甩石機弦這種武器，而是指使用武器的人，即「甩石者」。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt6:12\">JDT 6:12</a> 可譯作，「用甩石機弦作武器的人」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 直譯）。</p>\n<p>如果目標讀者不知道這種武器，翻譯者可以這樣表達：「一種用來甩擲石頭的特殊武器」。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
